{"tid":102858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"團體反對發展大型公園地下空間","createTime":"2017-02-01T01:51:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-02T03:09:43.000Z","uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8afa4c1ff87255c7899cbc0fdcc51320e2912e16","tid":102858,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:51:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s30.postimg.org/bthifwvxt/16387243_1200261810022882_7476079224295798808_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs30.postimg.org%2Fbthifwvxt%2F16387243_1200261810022882_7476079224295798808_n.jpg&h=dd95fea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府研究在市區多個大型公園，發展地下空間，興建行人通道等設施。<br />\n<br />\n有關注團體反對計劃，擔心影響休憩及綠化空間。<br />\n<br />\n他們指指施工期間除了影響市民使用公園，更可能需要斬樹、剷走草地，擔心當局為求開發商業空間，犧牲市民的休憩和綠化用地。<br />\n<br />\n土木工程署正展開公眾諮詢，研究在九龍公園、維園及修頓球場發展地下空間，興建行人通道，以及商業、文娛和社區設施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/622296951295710/?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F622296951295710%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DPAGES_TIMELINE&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZzM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=b399bb49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/622296951295710/?hc_ref=PAGES_TIMELINE</a><br />\n<br />\n其實開發地下空間，對於地產商是一件壞事。好多呢啲環保團體都係背後有地產商俾錢, 冇地方起樓、起舖頭可以囤積居奇買貴啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n環保觸覺曾令到一名教院學生反對大埔新發展起屋，玩司法覆核最終敗訴要賠過百萬。"},{"pid":"4cb1419306eb1a38e0f7625849b29474ef6ae240","tid":102858,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:53:23.000Z","msg":"日本咁多地震都整咁多地下街<br />\nBtw我都唔太鍾意行地底"},{"pid":"2e77f6d44ddfbff046ddb48be75111efbf8323f7","tid":102858,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:57:19.000Z","msg":"公園地底唔關地產事掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27285df7d96f36b9a0998d025d31b10984b67d00","tid":102858,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:59:36.000Z","msg":"都係咪攪<br />\n一來分分鐘又過千億<br />\n二來咪又係搞商場<br />\n就算你係搞公共設施，公園球場之類，到時你又話設施夠用可以拆地面啲球場公園起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0482916b8050f17ea5b222c9c89820e12aa64b","tid":102858,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"我支持<br />\n<br />\n為左環保  <br />\n長遠 看 使用地下空間是大勢所趨<br />\n<br />\n香港地表有限 要保留地表綠化(郊野公園等)  就一係向上 一係向下 一係向海"},{"pid":"b7e58119b6ea28b314cb426d4afe9d1594b5e43e","tid":102858,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係咪攪<br />\n一來分分鐘又過千億<br />\n二來咪又係搞商場<br />\n就算你係搞公共設施，公園球場之類，到時你又話設施夠用可以拆地面啲球場公園起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n關乜撚事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n政府起野要係政府地起丫嘛死撚蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87d1bb7318ee923ed945be0bdf29377b5ddd97f","tid":102858,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5730b7755b33f993c87f8ee8908bf4251f01dbcb","tid":102858,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"係咪想趕晒休閒人落地底，地面發展俾消費動物用？"},{"pid":"1b8ac50f3901b5c0928a522d695503321b0e7858","tid":102858,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"最左面既鬼妹好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cae7f7c9d14fa7848e81226644728205009cf5","tid":102858,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01